<li id="cite_note-10"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-10">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Michael Lambert, "Athens," in <i>Gay Histories and Cultures: An Encyclopedia</i> (Taylor &amp; Francis, 2000), p. 122.</span>
