<li id="cite_note-Greek_Homosexuality-46"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Greek_Homosexuality_46-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Greek_Homosexuality_46-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Greek_Homosexuality_46-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFKenneth_Dover1978" class="citation book cs1">Kenneth Dover (1978). <span class="id-lock-registration" title="Free registration required"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/details/greekhomosexuali00dove_0"><i>Greek Homosexuality</i></a></span>. United States: Harvard University Press. p.&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/details/greekhomosexuali00dove_0/page/20">20</a>. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0674362616" title="Special:BookSources/0674362616"><bdi>0674362616</bdi></a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Greek+Homosexuality&amp;rft.place=United+States&amp;rft.pages=20&amp;rft.pub=Harvard+University+Press&amp;rft.date=1978&amp;rft.isbn=0674362616&amp;rft.au=Kenneth+Dover&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Fgreekhomosexuali00dove_0&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APederasty+in+ancient+Greece" class="Z3988"></span></span>
