<li id="cite_note-78"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-78">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFShapiro1981" class="citation journal cs1">Shapiro, H. A. (April 1981). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220414024306/https://www.jstor.org/stable/505033">"Courtship Scenes in Attic Vase-Painting"</a>. <i>American Journal of Archaeology</i>. <b>85</b> (2). The University of Chicago Press: 133–143. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.2307%2F505033">10.2307/505033</a>. <a href="/wiki/JSTOR_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="JSTOR (identifier)">JSTOR</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/505033">505033</a>. <a href="/wiki/S2CID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="S2CID (identifier)">S2CID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://api.semanticscholar.org/CorpusID:192965111">192965111</a>. Archived from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/505033">the original</a> on 14 April 2022<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">14 April</span> 2022</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=American+Journal+of+Archaeology&amp;rft.atitle=Courtship+Scenes+in+Attic+Vase-Painting&amp;rft.volume=85&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.pages=133-143&amp;rft.date=1981-04&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.semanticscholar.org%2FCorpusID%3A192965111%23id-name%3DS2CID&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F505033%23id-name%3DJSTOR&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.2307%2F505033&amp;rft.aulast=Shapiro&amp;rft.aufirst=H.+A.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F505033&amp;rfr_id=info%