<li id="cite_note-80"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-80">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Percy, <i>Pederasty and Pedagogy in Archaic Greece</i>, p. 119; Nussbaum, <i>Sex and Social Justice</i>, pp. 268, 307, 335; Ferrari, <i>Figures of Speech</i>, p. 145.</span>
