<li id="cite_note-94"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-94">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Percy, William A. <i>Pederasty and Pedagogy in Archaic Greece,</i> , University of Illinois Press, 1996, pp146-150</span>
