<li id="cite_note-Perc-95"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Perc_95-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Perc_95-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Perc_95-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text">Percy, William A. <i>Pederasty and Pedagogy in Archaic Greece</i>, University of Illinois Press, 1996, p79</span>
